tooltip.formatter: function (params) { params = params[0]; var date = new Date(params.name); return ( date.getDate() + '/' + (date.getMonth() + 1) + '/' + date.getFullYear() + ' : ' + params.value[1] ); }

actions.name: Randomize
actions.handler: (chart) => { const data = sharedVar.data = []; sharedVar.now = new Date(1997, 9, 3); sharedVar.value = Math.random() * 1000; for (var i = 0; i < 1000; i++) { data.push(sharedVar.randomData()); } chart.setOption({ series: [ { data: data } ] }); }

sharedVar.randomData: () => { sharedVar.now = new Date(+sharedVar.now + sharedVar.oneDay); sharedVar.value = sharedVar.value + Math.random() * 21 - 10; return { name: sharedVar.now.toString(), value: [ [sharedVar.now.getFullYear(), sharedVar.now.getMonth() + 1, sharedVar.now.getDate()].join('/'), Math.round(sharedVar.value) ] }; }
sharedVar.setInterval: function (myChart) { return window.setInterval( function () { const data = sharedVar.data; for (var i = 0; i < 5; i++) { data.shift(); data.push(sharedVar.randomData()); } myChart.setOption({ series: [ { data: data } ] }); } , 1000); }
